snippet.title: Halfpipe Hero - Game Play Trailer
snippet.description:
Halfpipe Hero is an awesome arcade skateboarding game, grab your skateboard and rock the halfpipe! Tap to pull off sweet tricks and nail the landing. 
Get it here: http://j.mp/halfpipehero
